---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Career Transition Services | Compensation"
  description="Explore career transition services available through the UK Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Learn about retraining opportunities, job placement assistance, and support for starting a new career.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Career Transition Services for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) recognises the importance of supporting veterans in their transition to civilian careers. This page outlines the career transition services available to help you build a successful post-military career.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Skills Assessment and Career Counselling</h2>
        <p>Our career counselling services include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Comprehensive skills and aptitude assessments</li>
          <li>One-on-one career guidance sessions</li>
          <li>Assistance in identifying transferable military skills</li>
          <li>Exploration of suitable civilian career paths</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Retraining and Education Support</h2>
        <p>We offer various retraining opportunities:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Funding for vocational courses and certifications</li>
          <li>Support for higher education, including university degrees</li>
          <li>Access to online learning platforms and resources</li>
          <li>Apprenticeship programmes with veteran-friendly employers</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">CV Writing and Interview Preparation</h2>
        <p>Practical support to help you secure civilian employment:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>CV writing workshops tailored for veterans</li>
          <li>Interview skills training and mock interviews</li>
          <li>Guidance on translating military experience for civilian employers</li>
          <li>Personal branding and LinkedIn profile optimisation</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Job Placement Assistance</h2>
        <p>We provide comprehensive job search support:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access to a network of veteran-friendly employers</li>
          <li>Exclusive job fairs and networking events for veterans</li>
          <li>Partnerships with recruitment agencies specialising in veteran placement</li>
          <li>Mentoring programmes connecting veterans with industry professionals</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Entrepreneurship Support</h2>
        <p>For veterans interested in starting their own business:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Entrepreneurship workshops and boot camps</li>
          <li>Guidance on business planning and startup funding</li>
          <li>Mentoring from successful veteran entrepreneurs</li>
          <li>Access to small business resources and networks</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/support/mental-health" class="text-decoration-none">Mental Health Support</a></li>
              <li><a href="/financial/budgeting" class="text-decoration-none">Financial Planning</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/housing-assistance" class="text-decoration-none">Housing Assistance</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Career Transition Workshop</h3>
            <p>Join our upcoming workshop on transitioning to civilian careers. Learn valuable skills and network with potential employers.</p>
            <a href="/career-workshop" class="btn btn-primary">Register Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
